fields.name: stoic_arthur_schopenhauer
fields.quotes: Talent hits a target no one else can hit. Genius hits a target no one else can see.

fields.name: stoic_seneca
fields.quotes: Luck is what happens when preparation meets opportunity.

fields.name: stoic_marcus_aurelius
fields.quotes: You have power over your mind, not outside events. Realize this, and you will find strength.

fields.name: stoic_immanuel_kant
fields.quotes: Rules for happiness: something to do, someone to love, something to hope for.

fields.name: stoic_plato
fields.quotes: Books give a soul to the universe, wings to the mind, flight to the imagination, and life to everything.
